WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en-GB

00:00:07.720 --> 00:00:14.500
Welcome to UWSCollege. Let us take you on
a tour and give you a glimpse of campus life.

00:00:15.590 --> 00:00:21.269
Our campuses are well serviced by public transport
so if you want to visit the city or do some

00:00:21.269 --> 00:00:23.200
sightseeing it's easy. 

00:00:27.500 --> 00:00:30.269
And if you have a car
there's plenty of parking available on campus.

00:00:30.980 --> 00:00:35.660
All campuses have well equipped libraries
with all the resources you need and computer

00:00:35.660 --> 00:00:38.200
labs that you can use anytime free of charge.

00:00:39.700 --> 00:00:46.200
Each campus has a Student Centre where students can meet, study or just relax.

00:00:48.200 --> 00:00:51.190
There are lots
of activities for students - table tennis, Tai Chi,

00:00:51.190 --> 00:00:58.190
soccer, beach volleyball and lots more.
There is gyms to keep fit and a swimming pool.

00:00:58.900 --> 00:01:03.560
Kitchens are provided for students to use
or they can buy food and drinks from one of

00:01:03.560 --> 00:01:10.260
the many cafes and food outlets. The student
centre regularly organises lots of free events

00:01:10.260 --> 00:01:16.070
and social activities. Its great fun and an
opportunity to connect with other students.

00:01:16.070 --> 00:01:23.800
There are prayer rooms available on each campus
if you need some time for quiet reflection.

00:01:24.550 --> 00:01:30.549
UWS College is truly multi-cultural with students
from many different countries coming together

00:01:30.549 --> 00:01:36.680
to meet, make new friends and learn in a supportive
and friendly environment. If you need help

00:01:36.680 --> 00:01:43.000
with your studies or personal issues the Student
Advisers and Counsellors are always available.

00:01:43.190 --> 00:01:48.549
Student safety and security is a high priority.
There are emergency contact points on each

00:01:48.549 --> 00:01:52.600
campus and 24hr Closed Circuit Television
monitoring systems. 

00:01:54.000 --> 00:02:00.080
There are lots of clubs and societies available, so whatever your interest there's something here for you!

00:02:00.080 --> 00:02:05.560
At UWSCollege we care about our students' academic
success and their personal and social development.

00:02:05.560 --> 00:02:11.300
We want them to thrive, feel like they belong
and help them achieve their full potential

00:02:11.300 --> 00:02:14.800
while studying and living in Australia. 

00:02:15.600 --> 00:02:19.600
So why don't you join us, at UWSCollege.

